## What's Next

Day 25 translates today's enterprise risk picture into a practical management tool — the **Risk Register**. A risk register takes the identified risks, assigns them owners, documents their current status, and tracks remediation progress over time. It is the operational artifact that turns enterprise risk assessment from a one-time exercise into an ongoing management process.

